    <p class="description">The annualized value of your recurring subscription revenue. Calculated as <strong>MRR × 12</strong>. It is how SaaS companies get valued, funded, and benchmarked — public SaaS trades at <strong>5–15× ARR</strong>, and top-decile growers hit 20× or more.</p>
